{"tid":2021594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜「超甜預告」終於來了！俏皮模樣讓粉絲陷入瘋狂","createTime":"2020-05-17T23:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:35:12.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edacf90e85014e78a42f52c5d873d366f6715968","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/05/16/200516-13552-1-9QH52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F16%2F200516-13552-1-9QH52.jpg&h=31903e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睽違 9 個月，即將於 6 月 1 日發布第九張迷你專輯，經紀公司每日推出不同團員預告片，（16）日終於釋出子瑜專屬預告，只見花海中襯托俏皮模樣，堪稱人比花嬌！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>相關話題：</strong><br />\n<br />\n子瑜「超美複製」迪士尼公主！復古靚照曝光　網友：戀愛了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790122\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790122</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"20633e0d600a79813dbe84211a124c8c27b005bf","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/05/16/200516-13552-2-UzmEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F16%2F200516-13552-2-UzmEK.jpg&h=2fdcb35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">高馬尾露出性感肩頸處，也讓網友直呼：最適合綁馬尾的藝人！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"17a5abe60e59f12c642cffb50134a0b8839f2ace","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:06:35.000Z","msg":"即將在下個月推出全新單曲，經紀公司每日釋出不同成員預告片，讓粉絲頻頻敲碗許願，希望官方能盡快釋出子瑜版本預告內容，等了幾天後，不負眾望盼到了「超甜笑容子瑜版」，花團錦簇襯托之下，她的低頭萌笑彷彿化身春日仙女般，讓全網粉絲為之瘋狂！"},{"pid":"7f38b2599f3fa93cf40b762da645b656f03d12da","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/05/16/200516-13552-5-LAAc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F16%2F200516-13552-5-LAAc3.jpg&h=0bd490fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">九宮格的子瑜，每個畫面都讓人心動不已。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2c6d5d76abaddc07b91e1b6b3f9c2c5f33f73ee6","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:07:01.000Z","msg":"以復古鏡頭做為設計概念，子瑜以靈動輕盈身影出現在預告裡，春風輕拂的狀態下，舉手投足間流露出自信光彩，讓恬靜秀氣的臉龐也更顯女人氣質，最讓粉絲讚許的則是她一頭清爽馬尾，露出最性感的肩頸處，網友也紛紛留言表示：<em><strong>「請讓我們子瑜多綁馬尾好嗎」、「這種馬尾殺實在太誘人」、「周子瑜超適合綁馬尾」、「馬尾控秒淪陷」</strong></em>......！"},{"pid":"0616e3990c52f22c45c0ef1440bc0ba3ee9e4153","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/05/16/200516-13552-4-J71x7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F16%2F200516-13552-4-J71x7.jpg&h=33e71b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">也有網友表示等不及看到這次全員飛到濟州島拍攝的 MV、畫報。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"173158d4a48b34d6930f7793d3f7557f05271fbc","tid":2021594,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/05/16/200516-13552-3-6yQwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F16%2F200516-13552-3-6yQwu.jpg&h=96b2417e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">在花海的包圍，年輕有朝氣的俏皮模樣，令粉絲深受喜愛。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2340f222fd6233361e0fe2b0fe9433d18ef9394d","tid":2021594,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"